# KutunzaCare Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file to .env (in the same directory)
# 2. Fill in your actual values
# 3. Restart the Expo dev server after editing
# 4. NEVER commit .env to source control (it's in .gitignore)

# ─── Anthropic API Key ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com
# Required for: Kutu AI chat, Photo Food Log analysis
EXPO_PUBLIC_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# ─── Optional: Backend Proxy (for production deployments) ────────────────────
# If you want to keep the key server-side (recommended for public app stores):
# 1. Deploy a proxy server (see /server folder if present)
# 2. Set the URL below
# 3. Set USE_PROXY=true in src/config/api.ts
# EXPO_PUBLIC_PROXY_URL=https://your-backend.com/api
